<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>elementPrefixPath doesn't load from config and doesn't quite work. Here is the fix:</p>

<p>in Form.php setOptions method add:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
if (isset($options['elementPrefixPath'])) {
   $this-&gt;addElementPrefixPaths($options['elementPrefixPath']);
   unset($options['elementPrefixPath']);
}
</code></pre>

<p>And in Form.php addElementPrefixPaths method, change:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$this-&gt;_elementPrefixPaths[] = $this-&gt;_elementPrefixPaths + $spec;
</code></pre>

<p>to</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$this-&gt;_elementPrefixPaths = $this-&gt;_elementPrefixPaths + $spec;
</code></pre>

